name: ANN MICHELL SPORT LATEX WAIST CINCHER
description:
About Garment:

This garment is made to help you Lose Inches from your Abdominal Area. From the Initial Wear, you will Look 1-3 inches Smaller! The Thermo Iodized Latex Interior is the Secret to Getting the Perfect Hourglass Figure. It cultivates your body heat when worn which Promotes Sweating and Starts to Detox your Body of toxins. This process turns your body into a fat melting machine. The Aggressive Compression reduces your Appetite by Making you Feel Full on Less. The inner Flexi-Boning keeps the garment from "Rolling Up" & Losing it's shape. The garment features 2 levels of Closure to Size Down as you Lose Weight. The garment is Strong enough to Work Out in, yet Comfortable enough to Sleep in. This garment is Seamless under Fitted Clothing so you have No Worries!

Expected Results:

Lose 2-4 inches from your Waist. 
Lose 1-2 Dress Sizes. 
Flattened Back Fat & Rolls. 
Reduced Belly Fat & "Pooch".

How To Use:

Wrap the Garment around your Abdominal Area. 
Fasten the Hook & Eye Closure until the Garment is Fitted but Comfortable to Wear. 
DO NOT OVER FASTEN TO AVOID DAMAGE TO GARMENT. 
ASSISTANCE MAY BE NEEDED.

Recommended Usage:

Wear garment 8 or more hours a day. 
Workout in garment 3-4x per week for at least 30 mins. 
Sleep in garment for Continued Results. 
IT IS RECOMMENDED TO PURCHASE 2 TO ALTERNATE BETWEEN.

Garment Description:

Material: 
Exterior Layer: Natural rubber 100%. 
Interior layer: Natural rubber 100% 
Lining: Cotton 91%, Spandex 9%. 
Color: Pink, Purple  
Style: Cincher 
Item Number: 027

AUTHENTIC PRODUCTS IMPORTED FROM COLOMBIA.

NO RETURNS OR EXCHANGES PERIOD!!

name: Standard Steel Boned Underbust Corset
description:
Standard Underbust Pattern is Perfect for Long, Medium & Short Torso.

Front length is 11 inches (28 cm).

Underbust to bottom length is 9.7 inches (24.6 cm).

Side length is 9.5 inches (24 cm).

Back Length is 11.5 inches (29.20 cm).

Bone: 14 flat steel bones are distributed all around the corset.

Front opening is metal busk which is 9.5 inches long.

Lacing: It has 8 meter long lace which is used to tight lacing the corset.

Grommets in the back 8X 2 = 16 total.

Panels: It is made up of 12 panels, 6 on each half.

Modesty panel 6 inches wide. This will hide skin at the back.

Fabric Layer-1: Shell Fabric 100% Poly satin which is fused for strength.

Fabric Layer-2: lining 100% cotton which is fused for strength.

Waist tape: 1 inch wide satin waist tape is used for perfect grip and hold.

Suspender loops: 6 suspender loops at the bottom.

Bone casing: All bones are placed under cotton twill bone casing.


Important Information for Waist Training Corset:

Waist training is the process of permanently altering your figure by wearing heavy laced corsets for long periods of time (months). Although these garments may be suitable for waist training please be aware that there can be serious risks. Do not wear tight laced corsets when pregnant, it is very harmful to your baby. Waist training is not suitable for teenagers or adults who are still developing. We advise tightening these garments only on a rare occasion as over use can be very harmful to your body. If you have been waist training and notice a difference in your health, please consult a doctor.

NO RETURNS OR EXCHANGES PERIOD!!
